These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-5-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: water, tea, cola, soy-milk, lemonade
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: spy, satire, action, disaster, sports
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: jazz, punk, salsa, gospel, soul
The people use 5 different means of transport: trike, snowmobile, subway, motorbike, bike
 1. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
 2. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 3. the person watching satire movies is the person driving the motorbike##1
 4. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 5. the person watching action movies is in an odd position##4
 6. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 7. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 8. the person watching sports movies is in an even position##4
 9. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
10. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
11. the person watching satire movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
13. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
14. the person drinking tea is the person watching spy movies##1
15. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the fan of punk##5
16. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
17. the fan of soul is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4     |      5      |
| Beverage      | water  | cola | lemonade | tea    | soy-milk        |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | sports | satire   | spy | action |
| Music-Genre   | soul          | salsa  | punk   | jazz   | gospel  |
| Transport     | bike         | subway  | motorbike  | snowmobile       | trike    |

