 9. the person who's sport is cycling is the person drinking cola##1
10. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
11. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
12. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
13. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
14. the pakistani is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
15. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##5
